    {
      "lineNumber": 264462,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tそしてすっかり安心しきたった時に事件は起こった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And just when everyone had completely let their guard down, the incident occurred."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264463,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tパーティの日、バードが現れた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "On the day of the party, Bird appeared."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264464,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t人類を魔物を全てを制したランスに敵はいない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There was no enemy to Rance, who had conquered all humans and monsters."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264465,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tランスも安心しきっていた",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance was also completely at ease."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264466,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tＡ．バードはランスを襲おうとして、庇ったシィルを殺す",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A. Bird tried to attack Rance but killed Shīru who protected him."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264467,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tＢ．直接シィルを殺す",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "B. Kills Shīru directly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264468,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tシィルはまっぷたつになり死んでしまう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Shīru was split in two and died."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264469,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t注意：このパーティの時、クルックーは、女神アリスと会っています",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Note: During this party, Kurukū met the goddess Alice."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264470,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264471,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tシィルを抱きしめるランス、その手の中でどんどん体温を失い死にかけるシィル",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance embraces Shīru, who is rapidly losing body heat and dying in his arms."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264472,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tこら死ぬなーといっても流石に無理なのはランスから見ても明らか",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even though Rance says, 'Don’t die,' it’s clear to him that it’s hopeless."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264473,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tなんかそれなり感動的な事をいいながら死んでいく",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Shīru says something somewhat touching as she dies."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264474,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t事件は、それだけで収まらなかった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The incident did not end there."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264475,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t気絶していた美樹が目をさます、ビクビク痙攣しておかしい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Miki, who had been unconscious, wakes up trembling and convulsing strangely."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264476,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t魔王に覚醒しかけている、ヒラミレモンを無理に食べさせても駄目",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She is on the verge of awakening as the Demon King; forcing her to eat Hiramiremon doesn’t work."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264477,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tもう止めれない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It can no longer be stopped."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264478,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tせっかく人類の危機がさったと思ったのに、魔王が覚醒してしまうと",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Just when they thought the crisis for humanity was over, the Demon King awakens."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264479,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tまたふりだし、いやもっとひどい事になる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It returns to the starting point, or rather, it becomes even worse."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264480,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t美樹は鎖でベッドに縛り付けられている、とっても苦しそう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Miki is chained to the bed and looks very distressed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264481,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264482,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t早く対策を取らねばいけない状態。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They must take measures quickly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264483,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t魔王を殺せばなんとかなるかもしれないが、美樹を殺すなんて出来ない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Maybe killing the Demon King could solve it, but they cannot kill Miki."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264484,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tかといって魔王が動き出したら大変",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "On the other hand, if the Demon King starts moving, it will be disastrous."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264485,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t何か対策は・・と考えているが、もう時間が無い",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Thinking if there’s any countermeasure... but time is running out."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264486,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t\t魔王の説明",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Explanation about the Demon King."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264487,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t\t魔王は消滅しない、もし死んだらどこかで次の誰かが魔王になる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The Demon King does not disappear; if he dies, someone else somewhere becomes the next Demon King."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264488,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t\t魔王は自ら魔王を別の物に引き継げる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The Demon King can pass on his title to another by himself."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264489,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t\tただし、魔王を引き継げる者はほんの一部の特異な能力の者だけ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "However, only a very few with special abilities can inherit the Demon King."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264490,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t\t先代魔王もそれを探し、誰も見つからなかったので異世界の娘を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The previous Demon King searched for such a person, but finding none, chose a girl from another world."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264491,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t\t選択するしかなかった",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He had no choice but to select her."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264492,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t魔人ホーネットが言う、私が魔王を引き受けよう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The demon beast Hornet says, 'I will take on the Demon King.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264493,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t美樹が聞く、いいの・・ほんとうにいいの？と",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Miki asks, 'Is that alright... really alright?'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264494,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tホーネットは、すまない、本来なら異世界から貴方を呼ぶなどせず",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hornet says, 'I’m sorry. Originally, I shouldn't have summoned you from another world.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264495,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t私がちゃんと魔王になっておればよかったのにと",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "'I should have properly become the Demon King myself.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264496,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tあの時はまだ力が無かったが、今なら不可能でないはずだと",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "'I didn’t have the power back then, but now it shouldn’t be impossible.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264497,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tホーネットは魔王を引き継ごうとするが、出来ない・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hornet tries to inherit the Demon King, but cannot..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264498,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t能力不足で血を吐いて倒れる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She coughs up blood and collapses due to insufficient ability."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264499,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tホーネットがいない場合",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If Hornet is not around..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264500,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t代わりにミラクルが行う、魔王か、私が為るのがふさわしい",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Miracle replaces her, saying, 'Demon King? I am the suitable one to become it.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264501,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t当然、うまくいかない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Naturally, it doesn’t go well."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264502,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tもう駄目、殺すしかない・・誰も出来ないのなら私がやると",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It’s no good anymore; killing is the only option... If no one else can do it, I will."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264503,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t誰かが殺そうとするがランスが止める",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Someone tries to kill her, but Rance stops them."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264504,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t可愛い女の子を見殺す事は俺様はしない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I won’t let a cute girl die like that."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264505,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t魔王、特別な能力を持った者しかなれないんだろ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The Demon King can only be someone with special abilities, right?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264506,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tなら、俺だ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Then it’s me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264507,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t世界を征服した、やる事なくなったしな、魔王とかやってみたかったのだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I’ve conquered the world and have nothing else to do; I wanted to try being the Demon King."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264508,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tそれに魔王になればシィルも復活出来るかもしれない、一石二鳥だ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Besides, if I become the Demon King, maybe Shīru can be revived—two birds with one stone."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264509,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tみんなが止める間もなく、ランスは美樹から血を受けた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Before anyone could stop him, Rance took blood from Miki."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264510,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tしばらく、苦しんだが・・・魔王移譲を成功し魔王ランスが誕生した。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He struggled for a while but succeeded in the transfer of the Demon King, and Demon King Rance was born."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264511,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t「がははははははは」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Gahahahahahaha!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264512,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tランステーマが流れたまま、エンドロール",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The Rance theme plays as the end credits roll."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264513,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tこの時点では魔王ランスがどんな性格なのか、悪なのか、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "At this point, it’s unclear what kind of personality Demon King Rance has; whether he is evil,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264514,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tそれとも人間の心をもったままなのか",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "or if he still retains a human heart."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264515,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tどっちとも取れるような感じで",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It’s ambiguous and can be interpreted either way."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264516,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\tそして再び　ＡＤＶ画面に戻る",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And then, it returns again to the ADV screen."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264517,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t　魔王になったランス。偉そうにしている",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance as the Demon King. He is acting arrogantly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264518,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t　サテラがうやうやしく従う",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Satera respectfully obeys him."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264519,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t　誰かが報告、学者でもいいし、何か魔物将軍でもいい",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Someone reports—could be a scholar or a monster general."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264520,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t　「魔王ランス様に我ら忠誠を誓います」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We pledge our loyalty to Demon King Rance-sama.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264521,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t　「なんなりとご命じ下さい",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Please command me as you wish.\""
    }
  ]
}

